name: mega_loop_while_nested_when_accumulates_even_hits
section: codegen-control-loops
args: 
type: Bool
expect: True
description: while with nested when and modulo must count even loop indexes.
law: (= (with [i 0 hits 0] (do (while (< i 6) (begin (when (= (% i 2) 0) (set! hits (+ hits 1))) (set! i (+ i 1)))) hits)) 3)
